{"fields":[{"t":"B","v":"true","n":"HasPrompt"},{"t":"B","v":"false","n":"HasRevealPrompt1"},{"t":"B","v":"false","n":"HasRevealPrompt3"},{"t":"B","v":"false","n":"HasRevealPrompt4"},{"t":"B","v":"false","n":"HasRevealPrompt5"},{"t":"B","v":"false","n":"HasRevealPrompt6"},{"t":"B","v":"false","n":"HasRevealPrompt7"},{"t":"B","v":"true","n":"HasRevealJoke0"},{"t":"B","v":"false","n":"HasRevealJoke1"},{"t":"B","v":"true","n":"HasRevealJoke2"},{"t":"B","v":"true","n":"HasRevealJoke3"},{"t":"B","v":"true","n":"HasRevealJoke4"},{"t":"B","v":"true","n":"HasRevealJoke5"},{"t":"A","s":"Demonstriere dem Raum, wie du dich anhören würdest, wenn du von einer wirklich hohen Klippe fällst.","n":"RevealPrompt1"},{"t":"A","s":"Was ist etwas, das dich nicht stören würde, wenn es dich verfolgt?","n":"RevealPrompt3"},{"t":"A","s":"Wie bist du gestorben?","n":"RevealPrompt4"},{"t":"A","s":"Was glaubst du, was es bedeutet, von Käfern zu träumen, die unter der Haut krabbeln?","n":"RevealPrompt5"},{"t":"A","s":"Was ist das absolut schlimmste Fach, in dem man nackt sein kann?","n":"RevealPrompt6"},{"t":"A","s":"Wenn du deine verlorenen Zähne durch irgendetwas auf der Welt ersetzen könntest, was wäre es?","n":"RevealPrompt7"},{"t":"A","s":"Und dann schreiben wir auch noch eine Mathearbeit...","v":"joke6","n":"RevealJoke0"},{"t":"A","s":"","n":"RevealJoke1"},{"t":"A","s":"Du hast echt Mumm.","v":"joke7","n":"RevealJoke2"},{"t":"A","s":"Lauf!","v":"joke3","n":"RevealJoke3"},{"t":"A","s":"Und niemand ist gekommen.","v":"joke4","n":"RevealJoke4"},{"t":"A","s":"Das geht mir wirklich unter die Haut.","v":"joke5","n":"RevealJoke5"},{"t":"A","s":"Welcher Albtraum seid ihr?","v":"prompt","n":"Prompt"}]}